271
00:16:38.776 --> 00:16:42.776
And if I don't know, I won't be able to make my eyes with magic.

272
00:16:42.776 --> 00:16:44.776
I will have to learn it anyway.

273
00:16:45.776 --> 00:16:47.776
There is no other way.

274
00:16:47.776 --> 00:16:50.776
Because I want to see everything in this world.

275
00:16:55.776 --> 00:16:58.776
Master Kunal, what would you like to drink?

276
00:16:58.776 --> 00:17:00.776
Milk tea or without milk tea.

277
00:17:00.776 --> 00:17:02.776
Can I get some hot water?

278
00:17:02.776 --> 00:17:03.776
Sure.

279
00:17:03.776 --> 00:17:04.776
Oh, hey.

280
00:17:05.776 --> 00:17:08.776
Oh, wow! This magic is really amazing.

281
00:17:08.776 --> 00:17:11.776
For someone who doesn't know anything about magic, this is a big deal.

282
00:17:11.776 --> 00:17:12.776
What's the matter?

283
00:17:13.776 --> 00:17:14.776
What happened?

284
00:17:14.776 --> 00:17:15.776
What's the matter?

285
00:17:20.776 --> 00:17:22.776
Maybe I saw something.

286
00:17:22.776 --> 00:17:23.776
What did you say?

287
00:17:23.776 --> 00:17:24.776
Really?

288
00:17:24.776 --> 00:17:25.776
Are you telling the truth?

289
00:17:25.776 --> 00:17:27.776
It wouldn't be good if you lied to me.

290
00:17:27.776 --> 00:17:28.776
Wait, wait.

291
00:17:28.776 --> 00:17:29.776
I don't even know myself.

292
00:17:29.776 --> 00:17:41.824
I didn see anything properly Maybe I had a misunderstanding that I saw something I know that you are a gentleman who knows how to cheat But you don know how to make a fool of yourself You a fool Listen to me

293
00:17:41.824 --> 00:17:43.024
I think I saw the red color.

294
00:17:43.024 --> 00:17:45.324
Or I felt it with magic.

295
00:17:45.824 --> 00:17:47.824
Is this apple red?

296
00:17:47.824 --> 00:17:49.824
No, it's not red at all.

297
00:17:49.824 --> 00:17:51.624
Then it must be red.

298
00:17:51.624 --> 00:17:52.624
Right.

299
00:17:52.624 --> 00:17:53.824
