301
00:17:56.824 --> 00:17:57.624
You're right.

302
00:17:57.624 --> 00:17:58.824
Because I've never seen it before.

303
00:17:58.824 --> 00:18:01.624
You will learn slowly, my dear.

304
00:18:01.624 --> 00:18:03.624
