309
00:18:15.024 --> 00:18:17.624
You are absolutely right. You are amazing.

310
00:18:17.624 --> 00:18:20.224
This is really no less than a miracle.

311
00:18:22.224 --> 00:18:23.824
Can he see the colors?

312
00:18:23.824 --> 00:18:26.624
He is slowly starting to understand the colors.

313
00:18:26.624 --> 00:18:29.624
They are able to recognise colours one by one.

314
00:18:29.624 --> 00:18:31.624
So now they can see.

315
00:18:31.624 --> 00:18:35.624
They can recognise things that are very close to them.

316
00:18:36.624 --> 00:18:39.624
