317
00:18:39.624 --> 00:18:43.624
Yes. They can trace ink and recognise colours.

318
00:18:43.624 --> 00:18:48.624
They don't recognise letters, but they can recognise pictures and encyclopaedia.

319
00:18:49.624 --> 00:18:50.624
Very good.

320
00:18:50.624 --> 00:18:51.624
I'm sorry.

321
