335
00:19:43.624 --> 00:19:47.624
Miss Jenny will be here any moment. I will surprise her. I am sure of it.

336
00:19:48.624 --> 00:19:50.624
Then you must give it your all.

337
00:19:50.624 --> 00:19:52.624
Yes, that's what I thought.

338
00:19:52.624 --> 00:19:53.624
Uh, hey!

339
00:19:55.624 --> 00:19:57.624
What a thing, Master Kunon!

340
00:19:57.624 --> 00:19:59.624
Beautiful red, just like the eyes of a white rabbit.

341
00:19:59.624 --> 00:20:03.624
When I make them big, I can understand the colors better.

342
00:20:03.624 --> 00:20:06.624
So this ball is of deep red.

343
00:20:06.624 --> 00:20:07.624
Kunon.

344
00:20:07.624 --> 00:20:08.624
Oh.

345
00:20:09.624 --> 00:20:12.624
I've heard that you can see colors. Is that true?

346
00:20:12.624 --> 00:20:15.624
This beautiful voice like a cuckoo, like someone singing,

347
