can only be my mother's.

348
00:20:18.624 --> 00:20:21.624
Oh no!

349
00:20:25.624 --> 00:20:27.624
Please forgive me.

350
00:20:27.624 --> 00:20:29.624
No!

351
00:20:29.624 --> 00:20:31.624
Are you okay? Can you hear me, mom?

352
00:20:31.624 --> 00:20:33.624
How can you do such a bad deed?

353
00:20:33.624 --> 00:20:35.624
I did a bad deed?

354
00:20:35.624 --> 00:20:39.624
Listen Master Cron, all humans have a red blood color.

355
00:20:39.624 --> 00:20:41.624
Oh, I didn't know that.

356
00:20:41.624 --> 00:20:43.624
Now I will close your pocket money.

357
00:20:43.624 --> 00:20:45.624
Eco, you will not get paid for three months.

358
00:20:45.624 --> 00:20:46.624
Please don't do that.

359
00:20:46.624 --> 00:20:47.624
Please forgive me.

360
00:20:47.624 --> 00:20:49.624
Oh, no!

361
00:20:49.624 --> 00:20:50.544
Oh, no!

362
00:20:50.544 --> 00:20:52.544
Piku, get up.

363
00:20:52.544 --> 00:20:54.144
Where is your mind going?

364
00:20:54.144 --> 00:20:57.144
This boy is really different and scary.

365
00:20:57.144 --> 00:21:01.144
He will touch new heights of success.

366
00:21:01.144 --> 00:21:06.144
Maybe he will become the greatest magician in the world.

367
00:21:06.144 --> 00:21:10.144
He will get the greatest book of magic, Cerulean Sorcerer.

368
00:21:17.624 --> 00:21:22.624
I'm glad we didn't have to be afraid

369
00:21:22.624 --> 00:21:27.624
Make sure one by one

370
