The fate we lack is still unknown

371
00:21:32.624 --> 00:21:36.624
The middle of a miracle

372
00:21:36.624 --> 00:21:41.624
If it's a night of tears

373
00:21:41.624 --> 00:21:50.624
I'm going to be a little crazy, but I'm going to keep going.

374
00:21:52.624 --> 00:21:58.624
I'm sure I'll be guided by these days.

375
00:22:00.624 --> 00:22:06.624
Go see tomorrow, this world you don't know with your heart.

376
